12:44 - Defendant Angel Azael Gutierrezperez in court, in custody with attorney Ramneek Singh Button (eligible).  Gilbert Grant Thompson appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Interpreter Barerra appears, sworn. Defendant has received copy of Criminal Complaint and advised of rights, charges and penalties. Court finds probable cause. Court enters Not Guilty plea. RD & JT set. Court sets $1000 Cash bond with conditions:   Defendant shall not use/possess/control any controlled substances (without a valid prescription therefore) or drug paraphernalia, nor be in the presence of anyone who does.   The Jail shall permit Defendant to make a phone call at the county expense for bail purposes.  Return date scheduled for May 16, 2016 at 02:30 pm.  Jury trial scheduled for June 15, 2016 at 08:30 am.
